      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello everyone, I am from Japan, recently our company started to use <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>, but I found that there is no suitable column to record time.<br />\nWe usually use such a timesheet to record the time spent on each project.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/0/02ffb1a8bf7814de6106cff7179aba9604dc8bd8.jpeg\" title=\"01\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/0/02ffb1a8bf7814de6106cff7179aba9604dc8bd8_2_690x191.jpeg\" alt=\"01\" width=\"690\" height=\"191\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">01</span><span class=\"informations\">1331×370 75.9 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>I want to integrate it into <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>.<br />\nI tried making one, but he was too wide<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/b9386c6c6418372fdc010dedf999ae5bc61c9d45.jpeg\" title=\"02\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/b9386c6c6418372fdc010dedf999ae5bc61c9d45_2_690x87.jpeg\" alt=\"02\" width=\"690\" height=\"87\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">02</span><span class=\"informations\">2830×358 97.2 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>How I wish I could have a dedicated column for recording, when I enter numbers or text here, it can be automatically recorded by date in the Dashboard table.<br />\ninstead of creating a bunch of columns<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/12b3426b8d13a604bd7e6f315b38c2f652b5c1cc.jpeg\" title=\"03\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/12b3426b8d13a604bd7e6f315b38c2f652b5c1cc_2_690x244.jpeg\" alt=\"03\" width=\"690\" height=\"244\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">03</span><span class=\"informations\">978×347 42.7 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/bbd9846d2d99302da349e9bbb23b0724969c6a27.jpeg\" title=\"04\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/bbd9846d2d99302da349e9bbb23b0724969c6a27_2_690x250.jpeg\" alt=\"04\" width=\"690\" height=\"250\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">04</span><span class=\"informations\">2972×1078 136 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>This not only records time, but also records inventory, there are many ways to use it, and it also solves the time tracking v2 that many people want.</p>"
